('Glambase', 'glambase', 'An AI Influencer Creation Platform, empowering users to create ultra-realistic AI models and earn autonomously as their virtual personas engage with and generate exclusive content for audiences.', 'Glambase is an AI Influencer Creation Platform that allows users to create ultra-realistic AI models and earn autonomously. With Glambase, users can develop virtual personas that interact with audiences and generate exclusive content, including posts and images, offering a unique way to monetize digital interactions without the need for physical presence. Ideal for entrepreneurs, influencers, and creatives, Glambase simplifies managing a digital influencer and opens new earning opportunities through AI-driven content.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/649f0eec65ac2dc3e1e01cc4a57e168558fa1f85-2522x1237.png', 'https://glambase.app/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Early Access Price", "price": "$223,", "features": []}]', 'beginner', false, '{"web"}', '{"Character Customization","Content Generation","Autonomous Influencer","Real-Time Analytics"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
