('GPTConsole', 'gptconsole', 'Revolutionize app development with AI agents for seamless automation.', 'GPTConsole is a cutting-edge AI tool designed to revolutionize the way developers interact with artificial intelligence. This platform is dedicated to creating, sharing, and monetizing AI agents, offering specialized AI workers that not only provide information but also perform tasks for extended periods. With its focus on simplifying complex AI agent development processes—such as event chaining, lifecycle management, and memory handling—GPTConsole empowers developers to concentrate on setting agent objectives. This tool is particularly tailored for developers seeking to generate production-ready applications, build features for existing apps, and even create animated doodles.', 'https://cdn.futurepedia.io/2026-02-27T11-18-21.499Z-gP-Wf-D-zJLvNTiw9m1i83lO7pWvhJzt9.png', 'https://www.gptconsole.ai/', 'freemium', '[{"plan": "Free Credits on Sign-Up", "price": "Free", "features": []}, {"plan": "Flexi-Plan", "price": "$1", "features": []}]', 'intermediate', false, '{"web"}', '{"Developer-Focused Platform","Flexible Data Infrastructure","Customizable AI Solutions","Seamless Integration"}', '{}', true, '{}', '{}', '', now()),
